{
  "texts": [
    "Designing efficient traffic engineering algorithms that can handle diverse traffic patterns is a challenging task.",
    "Adopting new optimization algorithms can be very motivating for future studies.",
    "Optimization algorithms such as greedy [92], particle swarm [6], Ant colony [101], Lion Swarm [84], and grey wolf [56] are effective for many-objective problems in load-balancing.Future Direction 4.",
    "Application-based load-balancing: Although the smart city is a widely used application in research papers and real-world scenarios, some other applications, such as healthcare and industry have been less studied.",
    "Exploration of data and extraction of information in such applications can be considered an interesting open topic for future studies."
  ]
}